	dprr:hasNoteText "When Metellus was elected and allotted to the Quaestio de repetundis, Verres became anxious to prolong his trial into 69 (Cic. Verr. 1.21 and 23 and 26-31; Ps.-Ascon. 212-215, and 217 Stangl; Schol. Gron. 337, and 350 Stangl)." .
